high_descs: Turn to the right and go the corner of the counter.
Pick up the potato from the counter.
Carry the potato and turn around, then right to find the microwave.
Place the potato in the microwave, turn it on. Take the potato out of the microwave.
Hold the potato and turn to the right to find the fridge.
Place the potato in the fridge.
Walk to your right to the corner of the counter.
Pick up the potato on the counter top
Turn around and walk to the microwave over the stove.
Put the potato in the microwave next to the white cup, cook it, and take it back out.
Walk to the refrigerator on your left.
Put the potato in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot potato in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Move to the corner of the counter to the left of you
Pick up the potato from the counter
Move to the microwave behind you
Heat the potato and retrieve it closing the door afterwards
Move to the fridge to the right of you
Place the potato in the fridge and close the door
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the fridge.
